    Immediate blitter with @{"QWB=QUICKWAITBLIT/S" link qwb} option.

    It loads the @{"quicklayers.library" link quicklayers} to speed up layers.library.

    It replaces Auto Interrupts routines with faster ones.
    It replaces BLIT, PORTS, SOFTINT interrupt routines.

    These patches do not interfere with other programs like:
    FBlit, SysPatch (best if you run SystemPatch after it), MCP (you have to disable QuickLayers patch),
    PoolMem (and other memory allocation patches), Executive.

    NOTE: SystemPatch takes care of your CPU and installs approriate patches.

